                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Not for somebody who is obsessed with Harry Potter</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
                      <span>2</span>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Helpful: </span>
                      <span>2</span>
